Home page                              g  inventory/
Create order                           gp inventory/order/create-new
Receiving general page                 g  inventory/receiving
Each order page                        g  inventory/order/<id>
Receive item(s) order-independent      gp inventory/receiving/receive-items
Inventory update page                  gp inventory/update
Order general page                     g  inventory/orders
Each order receiving page              gp inventory/receiving/<orderid>
Each order amending page               gp inventory/order/<id>/update
Each order deleting page               gp inventory/order/<id>/remove
All items page                         g  inventory/items
(show in-stock, on-order, arranged by category) 
Each item page                         g  inventory/item/<id>
Each item amending page                gp inventory/item/<id>/update
Each item deleting page                gp inventory/item/<id>/remove
Create new item page                   gp inventory/item/create-new
Create new category page               gp inventory/category/create-new
Each category amending page            gp inventory/category/<id>/update
Each category deleting page            gp inventory/category/<id>/remove
Each category viewing page             g  inventory/category/<id>

